#. module: tk_insurance_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:tk_insurance_management.insurance_policy_has_expired_mail_template
msgid ""
"<p>\n"
"                    <h4>\n"
"                        Dear,\n"
"                        <br>\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.policy_holder_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                    </h4>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    We hope this email finds you well. We are writing to provide you with important information related\n"
"                    to your insurance policy with\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    We want to keep you informed about the status of your insurance policy and ensure that you have all\n"
"                    the necessary details readily available. Our records indicate that there have been recent updates or\n"
"                    changes pertaining to your policy.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <table>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td colspan=\"2\">\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Please find below the key details related to your insurance policy:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Policy Number:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_number\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Policy:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_policy_id.policy_name\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Policy Category:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_category_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Policy Sub Category:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_sub_category_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Coverage Start Date:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.issue_date\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Coverage End Date:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.expiry_date\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Premium Amount:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <span t-field=\"object.total_policy_amount\"></span>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                </table>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    It is crucial to review the above information carefully to ensure its accuracy. If you have any\n"
"                    questions or concerns regarding the policy details, please reach out to our dedicated customer\n"
"                    support team at\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    or reply to this email. Our team will be happy to assist you.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    We strive to provide you with comprehensive coverage and exceptional service. Should you require any\n"
"                    updates or modifications to your policy, please inform us at your earliest convenience. We will\n"
"                    work diligently to accommodate your requests and ensure that your insurance policy aligns with your\n"
"                    evolving needs.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    At\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    we value your trust and are committed to your satisfaction. We appreciate your continued support\n"
"                    and look forward to serving you as your trusted insurance provider.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Thank you for your attention to this matter.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <t t-if=\"object.is_auto_cancellation\">\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            Note:\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                        Please be reminded that your insurance policy is due for renewal from expiry date\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.expiry_date\"></t>\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                        to cancellation date\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.cancellation_date\"></t>\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                        between\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_expiry_days\"></t>\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                        days. Failure to renew may result in policy cancellation. Act now to ensure\n"
"                        uninterrupted coverage.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                </t>\n"
"                <h5>\n"
"                    Sincerely,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.responsible_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                </h5>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <span>\n"
"                    <h4>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </h4>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.email\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.website\"></t>\n"
"                </span>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"<p>\n"
"                    <h4>\n"
"                        Querida,\n"
"                        <br>\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.policy_holder_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                    </h4>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Esperamos que este e-mail encontre você bem. Estamos escrevendo para fornecer informações importantes relacionadas\n"
"                    à sua apólice de seguro com\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                   Queremos mantê-lo informado sobre o status da sua apólice de seguro e garantir que você tenha todos\n"
"                    os detalhes necessários prontamente disponíveis. Nossos registros indicam que houve atualizações recentes ou\n"
"                    alterações relativas à sua política.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <table>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td colspan=\"2\">\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Veja abaixo os principais detalhes relacionados à sua apólice de seguro:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Número da apólice:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_number\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Política:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_policy_id.policy_name\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Categoria de política:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_category_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Subcategoria de política:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_sub_category_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Data de início da cobertura:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.issue_date\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                               Data de término da cobertura:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.expiry_date\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                               Valor do prêmio:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <span t-field=\"object.total_policy_amount\"></span>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                </table>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    É crucial revisar cuidadosamente as informações acima para garantir sua precisão. Se você tiver algum\n"
"                    dúvidas ou preocupações sobre os detalhes da política, entre em contato com nosso cliente dedicado\n"
"                    equipe de suporte em\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    ou responda a este e-mail. Nossa equipe terá prazer em ajudá-lo.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Nós nos esforçamos para fornecer a você uma cobertura abrangente e um serviço excepcional. Caso você precise de algum\n"
"                    atualizações ou modificações em sua política, informe-nos o mais rápido possível. Vamos\n"
"                    trabalhe diligentemente para acomodar suas solicitações e garantir que sua apólice de seguro esteja alinhada com suas\n"
"                   necessidades em evolução.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    No\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    valorizamos sua confiança e estamos comprometidos com sua satisfação. Agradecemos seu apoio contínuo\n"
"                    e esperamos atendê-lo como seu provedor de seguros confiável.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Obrigado pela sua atenção a este assunto.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <t t-if=\"object.is_auto_cancellation\">\n"
"                    <p>\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            Observação:\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                        Lembre-se de que sua apólice de seguro deverá ser renovada a partir da data de vencimento\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.expiry_date\"></t>\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                        até a data do cancelamento\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.cancellation_date\"></t>\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                        entre\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_expiry_days\"></t>\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                        dias. A não renovação pode resultar no cancelamento da apólice. Aja agora para garantir\n"
"                        cobertura ininterrupta.\n"
"                    </p>\n"
"                </t>\n"
"                <h5>\n"
"                    Sinceramente,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.responsible_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                </h5>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <span>\n"
"                    <h4>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </h4>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.email\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.website\"></t>\n"
"                </span>\n"
"            "

#. module: tk_insurance_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:tk_insurance_management.upcoming_invoice_installment_mail_template
msgid ""
"<p>\n"
"                    <h4>\n"
"                        Dear,\n"
"                        <br>\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.policy_holder_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                    </h4>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    We hope this email finds you well. We would like to bring to your attention that your next insurance\n"
"                    installment invoice is scheduled to be issued soon. It's important to us that you stay informed\n"
"                    about your policy payments to ensure continuous coverage.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <table>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td colspan=\"2\">\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Here are the key details of your upcoming installment:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Policy Number:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_number\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Policy:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_policy_id.policy_name\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Installment Date:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-esc=\"datetime.date.today() + relativedelta(days=object.reminder_days)\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Installment Amount:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <span t-field=\"object.monthly_installment\"></span>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                </table>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Please be prepared to make the payment by the due date to avoid any interruption in your coverage.\n"
"                    Ensuring your policy remains active is crucial for your protection and peace of mind.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    If you have any questions regarding your policy or payment options, please feel free to reach out to\n"
"                    our customer service team at\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    . We are here to assist you and address any concerns you may have.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Thank you for choosing\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    . We appreciate your trust in us and look forward to\n"
"                    continuing to serve your insurance needs.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <h5>\n"
"                    Best regards,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.responsible_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                </h5>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <span>\n"
"                    <h4>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </h4>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.email\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.website\"></t>\n"
"                </span>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"<p>\n"
"                    <h4>\n"
"                        Querida,\n"
"                        <br>\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.policy_holder_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                    </h4>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Esperamos que este e-mail encontre você bem. Gostaríamos de chamar a sua atenção que o seu próximo seguro\n"
"                    a fatura parcelada está programada para ser emitida em breve. É importante para nós que você se mantenha informado\n"
"                    sobre os pagamentos da sua apólice para garantir cobertura contínua.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <table>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td colspan=\"2\">\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Aqui estão os principais detalhes de sua próxima parcela:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                               Número da apólice:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_number\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Política:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.insurance_policy_id.policy_name\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Data de parcelamento:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <t t-esc=\"datetime.date.today() + relativedelta(days=object.reminder_days)\"></t>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                    <tr>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <strong>\n"
"                                Valor da parcela:\n"
"                            </strong>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                        <td>\n"
"                            <span t-field=\"object.monthly_installment\"></span>\n"
"                        </td>\n"
"                    </tr>\n"
"                </table>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Esteja preparado para efetuar o pagamento na data de vencimento para evitar qualquer interrupção em sua cobertura.\n"
"                    Garantir que sua apólice permaneça ativa é crucial para sua proteção e tranquilidade.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Se você tiver alguma dúvida sobre sua política ou opções de pagamento, sinta-se à vontade para entrar em contato com\n"
"                    nossa equipe de atendimento ao cliente em\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    . Estamos aqui para ajudá-lo e resolver quaisquer preocupações que você possa ter.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Obrigado por escolher\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    . Agradecemos sua confiança em nós e esperamos\n"
"                    continuando a atender às suas necessidades de seguro.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <h5>\n"
"                    Atenciosamente,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.responsible_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                </h5>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <span>\n"
"                    <h4>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </h4>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.email\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.website\"></t>\n"
"                </span>\n"
"            "

#. module: tk_insurance_management
#: model:mail.template,body_html:tk_insurance_management.insurance_policy_cancel_mail_template
msgid ""
"<p>\n"
"                    <h4>\n"
"                        Dear,\n"
"                        <br>\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.policy_holder_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                    </h4>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    We regret to inform you that your insurance policy with\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    policy number\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.insurance_number\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    will be canceled due to our inability to renew it.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Effective\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.cancellation_date\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    your coverage will be terminated, and you will not be insured under our policies thereafter.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    For further assistance or inquiries, please contact our customer service team at\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    or reply to this email.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Thank you for your understanding.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <h5>\n"
"                    Sincerely,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.responsible_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                </h5>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <span>\n"
"                    <h4>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </h4>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.email\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.website\"></t>\n"
"                </span>\n"
"            "
msgstr ""
"<p>\n"
"                    <h4>\n"
"                        Querida,\n"
"                        <br>\n"
"                        <strong>\n"
"                            <t t-out=\"object.policy_holder_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                        </strong>\n"
"                    </h4>\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Lamentamos informar que sua apólice de seguro com\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                   número da apólice\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.insurance_number\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                   será cancelado devido à nossa incapacidade de renová-lo.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Eficaz\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.cancellation_date\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    sua cobertura será encerrada e você não estará segurado sob nossas apólices posteriormente.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Para mais assistência ou dúvidas, entre em contato com nossa equipe de atendimento ao cliente em\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    ou responda a este e-mail.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <p>\n"
"                    Obrigado pela sua compreensão.\n"
"                </p>\n"
"                <h5>\n"
"                    Sinceramente,\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.responsible_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                </h5>\n"
"                <hr>\n"
"                <span>\n"
"                    <h4>\n"
"                        <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.name\"></t>\n"
"                    </h4>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.phone\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.email\"></t>\n"
"                    <br>\n"
"                    <t t-out=\"object.policy_provider_cmp_id.website\"></t>\n"
"                </span>\n"
"            "

